description:
Guests: Al Weaver, National Political reporter at the Hill, Calvin Schnure, Senior Economist at Nareit, Al Mottur, Democratic Strategist and Partner at Brownstein, Hyatt, Farber & Schreck, Former Ohio Republican Congressman Jim Renacci, and Guy Snodgrass, CEO of Defense Analytics, former director of communications and chief speechwriter to Secretary of Defense James Mattis.
